Vendor/scintilla/win32/
Vendor/scintilla/gtk/
Vendor/scintilla/qt/
Vendor/scintilla/scripts/

# Vendored Lexilla — same idea: skip docs / tests / Windows-only / examples.
Vendor/lexilla/doc/
Vendor/lexilla/test/
Vendor/lexilla/examples/
Vendor/lexilla/scripts/
Vendor/lexilla/access/

